troparia.text:
Through the Tree Adam was exiled from Paradise;
but through the Tree of the Cross the thief entered Paradise.
The first tasted of the forbidden fruit and disobeyed the Commandment;
but the second, crucified with Thee, confessed Thee as God.
"Remember me, O Lord, in Thy Kingdom!"

kontakion.text:
Come, let us all sing the praises of Him Who was crucified for us,
for Mary said when she beheld Him on the Tree:
"Though Thou dost endure the Cross, Thou art my Son and my God!"
